Package: trademetrics
Title: Performance and Risk Analytics for Trading Strategies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Traderverse", "Team", , "team@traderverse.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Calculate performance metrics, risk measures, and generate
    comprehensive analytics for quantitative trading strategies. Includes
    return metrics (CAGR, annualized returns), risk-adjusted metrics (Sharpe,
    Sortino, Calmar ratios), drawdown analysis, and rolling statistics.
    Part of the Traderverse ecosystem for quantitative trading in R.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    stats
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Remotes:
    Traderverse/tradeengine,
    Traderverse/tradeio,
    Traderverse/tradefeatures,
    Traderverse/tradeviz
URL: https://github.com/Traderverse/trademetrics,
    https://traderverse.github.io/trademetrics/
BugReports: https://github.com/Traderverse/trademetrics/issues
